---
title: Seared Lamb Rump & Parsnip Mash with Creamy Honey Mustard Sauce
description: What's the secret to moist, tender and extra-tasty lamb? Use a cut with the cap of fat still on, so the meat stays juicy while roasting. Bring
extra flavour with a creamy honey mustard sauce, plus some parsnip mash and you've got a restaurant-quality dish made by yours truly.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lamb-rump-parsnip-mash-c7bc2030.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/lamb-rump-parsnip-mash-60cc2810fd790439272773c3-35f06c90.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/seared-lamb-rump-and-parsnip-mash-60cc2810fd790439272773c3
course: main course
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: Modern
nutrition:
  fat: 66.4 g
